OL,3,CSecurity service opt-out in
OL,4,CHillsborough Law amendment 'too
OL,5,Cbroad', mayors warn
OL,7,FThe mayors of Liverpool and Manchester
OL,8,Fhave called on the Government to
OL,9,Fwithdraw an amendment to the
OL,10,FHillsborough Law that "creates too
OL,11,Fbroad an opt-out" for the security
OL,12,Fservices.
OL,14,FLiverpool City Region mayor Steve
OL,15,FRotheram and Greater Manchester mayor
OL,16,FAndy Burnham said the amendment "risks
OL,17,Fundermining the spirit of the
OL,18,Flegislation".
