OL,4,CHillsborough Law amendment 'too
OL,5,Cbroad', mayors warn
OL,7,FAmendments proposed by the Government
OL,8,Fon Wednesday brought security services
OL,9,Fwithin the scope of the legislation,
OL,10,Fsubject to the approval of the head of
OL,11,Ftheir service.
OL,13,FHowever, campaigners have argued this
OL,14,Fwould allow those running the security
OL,15,Fservices to decide whether to disclose
OL,16,Finformation.
