OL,4,CHillsborough Law amendment 'too
OL,5,Cbroad', mayors warn
OL,7,FSome had warned that a draft version
OL,8,Fof the legislation ` formally known as
OL,9,Fthe Public Office (Accountability)
OL,10,FBill ` might allow intelligence chiefs
OL,11,Fto "hide serious failures behind a
OL,12,Fvague claim of national security".
OL,14,FMr Rotheram and Mr Burnham said they
OL,15,Fhad "both seen devastating incidents
OL,16,Fin our regions and would never support
OL,17,Fanything which compromises national
OL,18,Fsecurity".
