OL,3,CSecurity service opt-out in
OL,4,CHillsborough Law amendment 'too
OL,5,Cbroad', mayors warn
OL,7,F"We appreciate that the government has
OL,8,Fmade huge strides in working to
OL,9,Fdeliver the Hillsborough Law and are
OL,10,Fgrateful for their willingness to work
OL,11,Fwith campaigners thus far to make it
OL,12,Fthe strongest law possible.
OL,14,F"It is in that spirit that we call on
OL,15,Fthem to withdraw their amendment ahead
OL,16,Fof Monday's debate and work with the
OL,17,Ffamilies and the Hillsborough Law Now
OL,18,Fcampaign to find a solution acceptable
OL,19,Fto all sides."
