OL,7,FHe said it should be up to the head of
OL,8,Fan inquiry to decide whether
OL,9,Finformation was relevant, adding there
OL,10,Fwere already national security
OL,11,Fexemptions that allowed evidence to be
OL,12,Fheard in private.
OL,14,FCampaigners have pointed to the 2017
OL,15,FManchester Arena bombing, which Labour
OL,16,FMP Anneliese Midgley told the Commons
OL,17,Fhad seen MI5 spend "six years
OL,18,Fmisleading the public and concealing
OL,19,Finformation".
