OL,7,FResponding to Ms Midgley on Wednesday,
OL,8,FSir Keir Starmer said he had "always
OL,9,Fbeen clear the duty of candour applies
OL,10,Fto the intelligence services" and
OL,11,Finsisted proposed amendments to the
OL,12,FBill did not water it down.
OL,14,FLiverpool West Derby MP Ian Byrne has
OL,15,Falso tabled several amendments of his
OL,16,Fown that would mean duty of candour
OL,17,Fapplies not only to intelligence
OL,18,Forganisations but also to people who
OL,19,Fwork for them.
