OL,7,FThe Hillsborough Law takes its name
OL,8,Ffrom the 1989 stadium crush in
OL,9,FSheffield, which led to the death of
OL,10,F97 football fans at the FA Cup semi-
OL,11,Ffinal between Liverpool and Nottingham
OL,12,FForest.
OL,14,FA Government spokesperson said: "This
OL,15,Flegislation will right the wrongs of
OL,16,Fthe past, changing the balance of
OL,17,Fpower to ensure the state can never
OL,18,Fhide from the people it should serve
OL,19,Fand putting a legal duty on officials
OL,20,Fto respond openly and honestly when
OL,21,Fthings go wrong.
